            "content": "<p>We are thrilled to have the <strong>Scottish Book Trust </strong>partnering with us for Stories for Schools!</p><p>The Scottish Book Trust is a national charity dedicated to changing lives through reading, writing, and books. One of their key messages is simple but powerful: <a href=\"https://www.scottishbooktrust.com/articles/all-reading-is-good-reading-audiobooks\" title=\"All Reading is Good Reading - Scottish Book Trust Blog\">all reading is good reading.</a></p><p>They are also the organisation behind the brilliant <a href=\"https://www.scottishbooktrust.com/authors-live-on-demand\" title=\"Author Live on Demand - Scottish Book Trust\">Authors Live</a> events, where they have interviewed some of the amazing authors featured on the Voxblock bookshelf.</p><p></p><p></p>",
